# My API

Defines response with a validation schema with 'Schema' keyword.

# List users [GET /users]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Body

            {
                "hello": "world"
            }

    + Schema

            {
                "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-04/schema#",
                "type": "object",
                "required": [
                    "hello"
                ],
                "properties": {
                    "hello": {
                        "type": "string"
                    }
                }
            }
